e.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Slipknot.-Credit-Jonathan-Weiner-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Slipknot">Slipknot</a>宣布与<a href="/artists/Knocked-Loose">Knocked Loose</a>等乐队一起举办“Here Comes The Pain”25 周年美国巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353"><b>活结乐队的小丑谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这支传奇重金属乐队即将庆祝其 1999 年首张同名专辑发行 25 周年。在他们的“Here Comes The Pain”巡演的北美站中，蒙面成员将在巴尔的摩、纽约市、多伦多、里奇菲尔德、英格尔伍德、奥斯汀、达拉斯等主要城市停留，然后返回家乡德斯爱荷华州莫因举行节结节。</p><p> Knocked Loose、Orbit Culture 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vended">Vending</a>都将在选定的日期提供开幕支持。 <a href="https://slipknot1.com/events/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Knotfest.com</a>的艺术家预售目前正在进行中，可以<a href="https://slipknot1.com/events/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处访问</a>。一般门票销售将于当地时间周五（5 月 3 日）上午 10 点开始。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fslipknot-tickets%2Fartist%2F763913" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>并查看下面的完整日期列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752481" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752481" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752481" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SLIPKNOT-25TH-ANNIVERSARY-TOUR-NORTH-AMERICA.jpg" alt="SLIPKNOT - 25 周年纪念巡演 - 北美 图片来源：PRESS" width="2000" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SLIPKNOT-25TH-ANNIVERSARY-TOUR-NORTH-AMERICA.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/